Download VmWare Center Converter

run it on the phisical machine you want to convert

Follow the instructions

THe program will take a while (almost 1 hour) and then it will create the .vdmk that you will be able
to import in virtualbox as virtual disk of another virtual os

Just create a new vm with the same os that the physical machine
Select as virtual hard disk the .vdmk that has been created

Check you settings (Enable APIC), network Settings

Then run it!

You will find the exact copy of your physical machine!

Now you can install Guest Additions!
